title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Youre liable to feel playful and frisky today, whether youre paired with someone or not. If youre single, flirt with no clear goals in mind other than for fun. But if youre happily attached, let your loved one know they are the most special person in the universe. You might even conspire about items on your bucket list you plan to cross off together. However, romance isnt meant just for lovers. Foster the kind of synergy that makes the world a sweeter place to be. Live life to the fullest; your joy is contagious. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
